_json.title: Latest News: Causes and Biomarker Of Lipedema
_json.gridTitle: Latest News: Causes and Biomarker Of Lipedema
_json.description: This is about a study by a research group in Australia. The paper is called: Key signaling networks are dysregulated in patients with the adipose tissue disorder, lipedema. It was published in the peer-reviewed journal International Journal of Obesity in November 2021.The authors were interested in not only learning about the molecular causes of lipedema but also finding an objective biomarker to identify this disease.
